      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOLLY ROSE (6) slotted in just off the lead from the wide box before lifting strongly to score (24.56) at this track in a Grade 5 over 435m. The form from her last run stacks up well. Looks to have an edge on most of these. DR. PATRICK (5) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (24.66) at this track behind Escaping Bindi in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Will give a great sight again. DR. GIANNA (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (25.12) in a Grade 5 at this track. Cannot be taken lightly. URGING (8) justified the favourite's tag last time and another big run is on the cards.",
